    {
      "id": "PopularPost30764",
      "post_content": "I use Spiteful Visions, Howling Mine, and Furnace of Rath. I've gotten it up to 10 damage a turn before I had to lightning bolt my way to victory, but it has a theoretical max of 64 damage per card. Every spiteful visions is 1 damage per card, and every furnace or rath doubles that damage. Get four of each... 1, 2, 3, 4, 8, 16, 32, 64. Then at that point they're drawing 5 cards per turn. Add 4 howling Mines, and its up to 9 cards a turn, that's almost 600 damage a turn. But in order to get that out without killing yourself is another story. ",
      "posted_by": "Schlorgadorb",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost30764\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I use Spiteful Visions, Howling Mine, and Furnace of Rath. I've gotten it up to 10 damage a turn before I had to lightning bolt my way to victory, but it has a theoretical max of 64 damage per card. Every spiteful visions is 1 damage per card, and every furnace or rath doubles that damage. Get four of each... 1, 2, 3, 4, 8, 16, 32, 64. Then at that point they're drawing 5 cards per turn. Add 4 howling Mines, and its up to 9 cards a turn, that's almost 600 damage a turn. But in order to get that out without killing yourself is another story. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '30764'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy14041\">Schlorgadorb</span>\r\n                                (10/19/2009 9:32:27 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.pn